Вакансія від 1 березня 2020
Content Marketing Specialist
12 500 – 25 000 грн
Rioks
Група компаній;
10–50 співробітників
Львів, вулиця Сербська.
0,2 км від центру ·
На мапі
Повна зайнятість, готові взяти студента, готові взяти людину з інвалідністю.
Досвід роботи від 2 років.
Опис вакансії
Rioks is looking for their new amazing team member. We’re a marketing consultancy working with clients all around the world in a variety of different industries. If you’re high energy, motivated individual who believes in crafting his/her own career path, then we might just be the thing you’re looking for.Rioks believes in hiring the best people and enhancing their skills by providing them with the most efficient tools for their job.We offer you the opportunity to have flexible, individual working hours while working from anywhere you would like. As a Content Marketing Specialist, we are looking for the following:Your Responsibilities:
Coordinating with internal marketing experts on the subject matter in order to distribute content marketing materials such as articles, press releases, white papers, infographics, blog posts, product descriptions, videos and etc.
Work closely with Marketing Strategists and SEO Specialists on the creation of content marketing campaigns.
You will be in charge of content outreach and media relations.
Lead content distribution campaigns including researching new marketing channels and influencer relations.
Track performance of content across multiple channels, communicate and report key information to management.
Use industry-trending tools to optimize the work process and achieve the most of performance from the content distribution and management process.
Analyze and improve campaigns based on the results of past marketing and content distribution campaigns.
Qualities We’re Looking For:
Fluent in English. No exceptions.
Previous experience in a similar position.
Strong self-management skills and ability to work remotely
Ability to multitask.
Ability to think analytically, out-of-the-box and to be a detail-oriented problem-solver.
Experience and a passion in the content creation and distribution.
If you believe you are a good fit for the position and can amaze — reach out!If you don’t meet the criteria above, but believe you can learn fast, we are keen to discuss the internship opportunities and individually develop scope of the responsibilities for specific employees.
